00:35:32,920 --> 00:35:34,160
this kid's got some nerve.

639
00:35:34,200 --> 00:35:36,200
- Well, how would he do it?
- He's needling me!

640
00:35:36,240 --> 00:35:37,800
He's gettin' in any way he can.

641
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:41,840
- I let him in.

642
00:35:43,160 --> 00:35:46,600
He had an order from
you, he used your name.

643
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:48,840
He was in our house.

644
00:35:50,760 --> 00:35:51,600
Oh, god.

645
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:54,360
Tom.

646
00:35:54,400 --> 00:35:55,840
God.

647
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:59,760
[classical piano music]

648
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:02,440
- How's the trial going?
