anything I say.

694
00:38:24,960 --> 00:38:26,520
I don't know what else to do.

695
00:38:29,080 --> 00:38:29,520
- Alright.

696
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:34,920
I wanna believe you, so I'm
only going to say this once.

697
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:37,680
If it's not you doing these
things, you can ignore it.

698
00:38:39,040 --> 00:38:43,920
