1010
01:02:05,560 --> 01:02:09,480
[suspenseful electronic music]

1011
01:02:30,880 --> 01:02:32,960
[knocks]

1012
01:02:36,560 --> 01:02:37,600
- [Tom] Echo sent me.

1013
01:02:38,960 --> 01:02:39,960
