1014
01:02:40,000 --> 01:02:41,200
That's real interesting.

1015
01:02:42,240 --> 01:02:43,120
Echo's away.

1016
01:02:46,480 --> 01:02:47,920
- [Tom] So was I.

1017
01:02:47,960 --> 01:02:50,280
Riverhead, I just got out.

1018
01:02:52,080 --> 01:02:55,400
- What do you want?
