we've been doing, you know,

1035
01:03:41,280 --> 01:03:44,080
the phone calls, credit
cards, changing the locks.

1036
01:03:44,120 --> 01:03:47,000
- Quit it.
- He's not gonna do anything.

1037
01:03:47,040 --> 01:03:48,640
- I really think I have to.

1038
01:03:48,680 --> 01:03:50,800
I've been thinking about
all those stereos, too.

1039
01:03:50,840 --> 01:03:52,280
Those ones that are
stowed at your house?

1040
01:03:52,320 --> 01:03:54,360
And then I have to admit that
I didn't see him do anything

1041
01:03:54,400 --> 01:03:56,920
to you in the alley, I was
lying the way you told me to.

1042
01:03:56,960 --> 01:03:59,560
But the toughest part is
going to be telling him about

1043
01:03:59,600 --> 01:04:02,320
the cradle, the way you two
left it in his bathroom,

1044
01:04:02,360 --> 01:04:03,880
after you trashed his place.

1045
01:04:03,920 --> 01:04:07,000
- He's not gonna believe that
crap, he knows it was you.

1046
01:04:07,040 --> 01:04:08,680
- I don't think so.

1047
01:04:08,720 --> 01:04:11,080
What if the police check the
fingerprints on the cradle?

1048
01:04:11,120 --> 01:04:13,560
They're yours, both of
you touched them,

1049
01:04:13,600 --> 01:04:15,600
after I wiped it clean.

1050
01:04:15,640 --> 01:04:17,320
- Uh-uh, no, we didn't.

1051
01:04:17,360 --> 01:04:18,200
- Are you sure?

1052
01:04:19,720 --> 01:04:20,560
Are you sure?

1053
01:04:21,680 --> 01:04:23,320
Are you sure?

1054
01:04:23,360 --> 01:04:25,000
You're not?

1055
01:04:25,040 --> 01:04:28,240
You were holding it and he
put the pig in.

1056
01:04:28,280 --> 01:04:31,160
I mean, you better be real
sure before you want out.

1057
01:04:33,040 --> 01:04:33,920
So?

1058
01:04:35,520 --> 01:04:36,520
What do ya say?

1059
01:04:39,280 --> 01:04:40,120
What?

1060
01:04:42,840 --> 01:04:43,640
- I'm in.

1061
01:04:46,520 --> 01:04:47,360
- Yeah.

1062
01:04:48,200 --> 01:04:49,040
- Perfect.

1063
01:04:53,200 --> 01:04:54,880
Hey, oink oink.

1064
01:05:24,240 --> 01:05:27,200
[suspenseful music]

1065
01:05:44,680 --> 01:05:47,040
- [Tom] I don't know
what's happenin' to me.

1066
01:05:47,080 --> 01:05:49,960
I don't know what I'm doing.
