1067
01:05:50,000 --> 01:05:51,880
Don't do anything, back off.

1068
01:05:54,680 --> 01:05:57,160
Look I don't blame you, this
whole thing's been a nightmare.

1069
01:05:57,200 --> 01:06:00,360
But it's not about right and
wrong anymore, it's survival.

1070
01:06:00,400 --> 01:06:01,960
And you've gotta focus
on what's right.

1071
01:06:02,000 --> 01:06:04,240
Sally, you and the baby,
that's where it is.

1072
01:06:07,920 --> 01:06:08,800
- I bought a gun.

1073
01:06:11,400 --> 01:06:12,800
- Geez, Tom.
- I know.

1074
01:06:12,840 --> 01:06:14,760
I don't know what else to do.

1075
01:06:14,800 --> 01:06:17,640
- What you do is you
get rid of it now, man.

1076
01:06:17,680 --> 01:06:19,240
Then you go home, you get Sally,

1077
01:06:19,280 --> 01:06:20,680
and you go look for a
new apartment.

1078
01:06:20,720 --> 01:06:22,720
Get away from this mess
and start clean.

1079
01:06:27,720 --> 01:06:28,520
- Yeah.

1080
01:06:31,440 --> 01:06:32,280
Yeah.

1081
01:07:03,040 --> 01:07:04,040
[dramatic music]
[Sally screams]

1082
01:07:04,080 --> 01:07:06,160
- Shh, let's go!
- Go, go, go!

1083
01:07:06,200 --> 01:07:08,880
[Sally screams]

1084
01:07:11,680 --> 01:07:13,080
Come on, come on!

1085
01:07:14,000 --> 01:07:17,000
[suspenseful music]

1086
01:07:19,720 --> 01:07:20,560
- Honey?

1087
01:07:25,920 --> 01:07:26,760
Honey?

1088
01:07:36,240 --> 01:07:38,480
