- [Robotic Voice] If you
want to find the treasure,

1091
01:07:41,760 --> 01:07:43,640
follow the clues.

1092
01:07:43,680 --> 01:07:46,160
- If you touch her,
I'll kill you.

1093
01:07:46,200 --> 01:07:48,120
- [Robotic Voice] You'll
get the first clue

1094
01:07:48,160 --> 01:07:51,600
from the phone booth at
