- I'm waiting for one.

1099
01:08:11,400 --> 01:08:14,000
[man speaks foreign language]

1100
01:08:14,040 --> 01:08:15,400
[phone rings]

1101
01:08:15,440 --> 01:08:18,200
- [Robotic Voice] The men's
room at the Penthouse Bar.

1102
01:08:18,240 --> 01:08:21,360
Be there at six sharp or
the clue will be gone.

1103
01:08:28,840 --> 01:08:31,760
[moody rock music]

1104
01:09:07,000 --> 01:09:10,400
[moody electronic music]

1105
01:09:53,480 --> 01:09:54,960
- Give him 20 minutes.

1106
01:09:57,840 --> 01:09:59,400
[suspenseful music]
[knocks]

1107
01:09:59,440 --> 01:10:01,520
- Alright, just leave it
outside the door.

1108
01:10:01,560 --> 01:10:03,880
- [Man] No, I need a signature.

1109
01:10:03,920 --> 01:10:06,360
- I don't understand why they
didn't sign for it downstairs.

1110
01:10:06,400 --> 01:10:08,000
- Where's Jeffrey?
- I want you out of here.

1111
01:10:08,040 --> 01:10:09,680
- Where is he?
- What do you want from us?

1112
01:10:09,720 --> 01:10:10,680
- I want my wife!

1113
01:10:11,960 --> 01:10:13,120
He's got my wife!
- Mr. Casey, that's not true.

1114
01:10:13,160 --> 01:10:14,520
- Shut up!

1115
01:10:14,560 --> 01:10:18,800
You have no idea what is going
on here, who your son is.

1116
01:10:18,840 --> 01:10:20,600
- Mr. Casey--
- I know it's him!

1117
01:10:20,640 --> 01:10:23,000
He uses a computer voice,
but I know who it is.

1118
01:10:24,320 --> 01:10:27,000
[ominous tones]

1119
01:10:29,040 --> 01:10:29,720
She's pregnant.

1120
01:10:31,040 --> 01:10:32,560
- [Detective] Mr. Casey,
your wife's only been gone

1121
01:10:32,600 --> 01:10:33,960
a few hours.
- Oh, please.

1122
01:10:34,000 --> 01:10:35,480
She didn't leave her
underwear on the bed

1123
01:10:35,520 --> 01:10:36,960
with a knife sticking in it!

1124
01:10:37,000 --> 01:10:39,480
- Dan will check on that
when I take you downtown.

1125
01:10:40,360 --> 01:10:41,560
- He knows where she is.

1126
01:10:43,040 --> 01:10:44,120
- I don't!

1127
01:10:46,800 --> 01:10:48,160
I wish I could help you.

1128
01:10:53,840 --> 01:10:57,200
Look, maybe she just
went shopping.

1129
01:10:57,240 --> 01:10:59,600
There's sales all over town.

1130
01:10:59,640 --> 01:11:02,160
She'll probably just come
home loaded with packages.

1131
01:11:02,200 --> 01:11:05,760
- You shut your mouth!
- He's crazy, he's crazy!

1132
01:11:05,800 --> 01:11:08,200
Your wife probably never
even left the building.

1133
01:11:09,560 --> 01:11:11,480
- [Detective] Let's go.

1134
01:11:30,760 --> 01:11:34,800
[horn honks]
[dramatic music]

1135
01:11:34,840 --> 01:11:38,000
Suspect's on the ground,
heading east!

1136
01:11:38,040 --> 01:11:40,800
- We should have cuffed
him, okay, stay on him.

1137
01:11:40,840 --> 01:11:43,000
He bolted, you stay put!
- Where are you going?

1138
01:11:43,040 --> 01:11:43,960
- Maybe I can help.

1139
01:11:44,000 --> 01:11:45,400
- You're not going
near that man.

1140
01:11:45,440 --> 01:11:47,000
- He's heading to his house,
it's just through the alley.

1141
01:11:47,040 --> 01:11:48,760
- What do you mean?
- I've gotta see this.

1142
01:11:48,800 --> 01:11:50,400
- Jeffrey, what's going on?

1143
01:11:54,560 --> 01:11:57,560
[suspenseful music]

1144
01:12:10,240 --> 01:12:12,440
- [Robotic Voice] If you
want to find the treasure,

1145
01:12:12,480 --> 01:12:14,280
follow the clues.

1146
01:12:14,320 --> 01:12:17,760
You'll get the first
clue from the phone booth

1147
01:12:17,800 --> 01:12:22,800
at the corner of 20th street
and 10th avenue at exactly 5PM.

1148
01:12:25,480 --> 01:12:29,760
The men's room at the
Penthouse Bar, be there at...

1149
01:12:29,800 --> 01:12:32,560
