1153
01:12:51,320 --> 01:12:53,160
- Secure the building, now!

1154
01:12:53,200 --> 01:12:54,160
- We've got an incident here.

1155
01:12:54,200 --> 01:12:55,640
Perp's somewhere in
the building.

1156
01:12:55,680 --> 01:12:58,640
I want everybody cleared out
of the first and second floor.

1157
01:13:00,160 --> 01:13:01,480
- [Officer] Clear
across the street.

1158
01:13:01,520 --> 01:13:02,600
Make sure those
people stay back.

1159
01:13:02,640 --> 01:13:06,040
- I want everybody out of
this area, now!

1160
01:13:22,600 --> 01:13:25,280
- Who do we have?
