building we don't know of.

1163
01:13:29,800 --> 01:13:31,360
I'm gonna try and talk him out.

1164
01:13:36,400 --> 01:13:40,560
Mr. Casey, Tom, this
is Lieutenant McKnight.

1165
01:13:40,600 --> 01:13:43,280
Tom Casey, I need to talk to ya.

1166
01:13:47,160 --> 01:13:49,880
[dramatic music]

1167
01:13:53,640 --> 01:13:56,040
[Tom groans]

1168
01:14:03,440 --> 01:14:08,440
[sirens wail]
[helicopter blades whir]

1169
01:14:12,080 --> 01:14:14,160
- Anything you can tell
us about the building?

1170
01:14:14,200 --> 01:14:15,240
- There's a hallway
that goes straight

1171
01:14:15,280 --> 01:14:16,680
