1178
01:14:56,440 --> 01:14:57,440
She'll be alright.

1179
01:14:57,480 --> 01:14:59,120
- She was in a closet
in the basement!

1180
01:15:00,400 --> 01:15:01,640
- Gee, Mr. Casey.

1181
01:15:01,680 --> 01:15:03,880
