1191
01:15:33,520 --> 01:15:35,920
Are you gonna shoot me in
front of all these cops?

1192
01:15:35,960 --> 01:15:39,800
- That depends on you,
Jeffrey, get over here!

1193
01:15:45,440 --> 01:15:49,440
[siren wails]
[suspenseful music]

1194
01:15:49,480 --> 01:15:51,440
- Please, isn't there
something you can do?

1195
01:15:51,480 --> 01:15:52,280
Jeffrey!

1196
01:15:54,400 --> 01:15:55,320
Oh, my god.

1197
01:15:58,800 --> 01:16:00,280
