Holding their position.

1201
01:16:17,840 --> 01:16:19,280
- Hey.

1202
01:16:19,320 --> 01:16:21,280
- Alright, we can see him,
has he got anyone else?

1203
01:16:21,320 --> 01:16:22,880
- No, just the kid.

1204
01:16:22,920 --> 01:16:26,040
