1214
01:17:21,840 --> 01:17:26,680
- Let the ambulance go, get
her to the hospital, now!

1215
01:17:33,680 --> 01:17:37,440
- [Officer] Come on,
clear the way, let's go.

1216
01:17:40,920 --> 01:17:42,800
- Alright.
[suspenseful music]

1217
01:17:42,840 --> 01:17:43,760
Me and you.

