- [Detective] This was
in Sally's hand.

1223
01:18:29,360 --> 01:18:30,720
- Is this Jeffrey's jacket?

1224
01:18:32,560 --> 01:18:33,360
- Yes.

1225
01:18:34,760 --> 01:18:37,760
[suspenseful music]

1226
01:18:43,680 --> 01:18:47,520
- Tom, I think you're
an obsessive-compulsive.

1227
01:18:49,360 --> 01:18:52,040
You keep insisting that
I've done all these things.

1228
01:18:53,480 --> 01:18:55,280
But you don't have any proof.

1229
01:18:55,320 --> 01:19:00,200
