gun, you don't need any proof!

1230
01:19:00,240 --> 01:19:01,800
- Tom?

1231
01:19:01,840 --> 01:19:02,880
Tom, you see what I have here?

1232
01:19:02,920 --> 01:19:04,480
This is Jeffrey's jacket.

1233
01:19:05,880 --> 01:19:08,080
A torn piece of it was
in your wife's hand.

1234
01:19:09,280 --> 01:19:10,240
We got him, Tom.

1235
01:19:11,960 --> 01:19:13,480
- That's not mine!

1236
01:19:16,480 --> 01:19:17,520
- I saw you take it off.

1237
01:19:17,560 --> 01:19:20,240
- I was wearing it, but
it's not mine.

1238
01:19:20,280 --> 01:19:23,320
You see, Tom, here's
how it works.

1239
01:19:23,360 --> 01:19:25,440
I could say to you right now,
I did it.

1240
01:19:27,800 --> 01:19:29,760
