1241
01:19:29,800 --> 01:19:30,640
- Jeffrey!

1242
01:19:31,680 --> 01:19:33,640
Tell him the truth.

1243
01:19:33,680 --> 01:19:36,240
- See, they can't even talk
to me without my lawyer.

1244
01:19:42,680 --> 01:19:46,080
- Then I don't know how
else to stop you.

1245
01:19:47,680 --> 01:19:48,560
- Oh, god.

1246
01:19:52,800 --> 01:19:53,640
Please!

1247
01:19:54,560 --> 01:19:56,040
Mr. Casey.

1248
01:19:56,080 --> 01:19:56,960
I believe you.

1249
01:19:59,000 --> 01:19:59,840
